{"tid":543503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧巴美揚入「廠」誘因：阿爸欣賞雲加","createTime":"2018-01-28T14:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T10:34:31.000Z","uid":46892,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"965980b172d3bc6bcfa9898202840b7c0c78c5bd","tid":543503,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=9ZLfab60MJFe0WuPRHKg0DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a158d322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】如果奧巴美揚最終加入阿仙奴，與他的爸爸有關？<br />\n<br />\n據《星期日泰晤士報》透露，雖然奧巴美揚（Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang）加盟阿仙奴一事尚未成事，多蒙特與阿仙奴之間尚在討價還價，但如果該加蓬國腳最終入「廠」，或與其父有關。這是由於奧巴美揚的父親皮爾利也曾是足球員，並在80及90年代於法國效力勒哈弗爾及圖盧茲等球會，對法國籍的雲加甚為欣賞，認為若奧巴美揚能夠在雲加麾下作賽，有利其事業發展。<br />\n<br />\n此外，奧巴美揚自去年12月16日因紀律問題被多蒙特棄用後，昨日對弗賴堡的德甲聯獲得重召，並以正選掛帥，最終多蒙特2:2逼和弗賴堡，幸保1分。比賽期間，有球迷舉起寫上「沒有球員大於我們的球會」字句的紙板，向有離心的奧巴美揚抗議。<br />\n<br />\n賽後，奧巴美揚在社交網絡反擊，一句「恨我或愛我」，愛戴他的人會受落，恨他的人或會感到被挑釁。"},{"pid":"7e555c3ce5d92ba6b053d9fb79225d81fead9bd2","tid":543503,"uid":38189,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"雲加始終係最大嘅籌碼"},{"pid":"63b11e89d2018e29e49e4aebd657ce9f4f2bba36","tid":543503,"uid":24362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:55:21.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d18ea136d6ff956acba1b48feb93a81b174fce4","tid":543503,"uid":20197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"爺爺係法國地位有幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93990361d1a1aa89bdd2f182cdc9a71bf428c43","tid":543503,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"迷雲黨無處不在"},{"pid":"cdb40252e2e810f03f763c470ad203f204b3fcf2","tid":543503,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1588713d893fa5d46248d75cf540c038307013d","tid":543503,"uid":33730,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:04:04.000Z","msg":"雲加係法國既地位已經高過拿破崙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf704d3d51ea897fe1fa8e4962b2955a5754275b","tid":543503,"uid":41744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"雲加已經唔係足球教練咁簡單.."},{"pid":"4bdddb15b7ab85a66fc6bd5917f534ac9099377e","tid":543503,"uid":129924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93990361d1a1aa89bdd2f182cdc9a71bf428c43","tid":543503,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"迷雲黨無處不在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b7d1ac333cc459056355e491a16f3c1e7a049d","tid":543503,"uid":37240,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:21:08.000Z","msg":"雲加係一種精神，係一種代表"},{"pid":"9481360a496de5b5aeaa715fab5c08cc3f771a79","tid":543503,"uid":33864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf704d3d51ea897fe1fa8e4962b2955a5754275b","tid":543503,"uid":41744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"雲加已經唔係足球教練咁簡單.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:22:40.000Z","msg":"雲加不嬲係一個政治 策略家 多過領隊"},{"pid":"3b5e4cd08413c04510e57a695a80d44a12d64301","tid":543503,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1588713d893fa5d46248d75cf540c038307013d","tid":543503,"uid":33730,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:04:04.000Z","msg":"雲加係法國既地位已經高過拿破崙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"雲加差一步就做到歐洲霸主<img sr